text: Fréhel is a commune. It is found in the region Bretagne in the Côtes-d'Armor department in the west of France. ==Twin towns== Fréhel is twinned with: * Mafra, Portugal ==Sport== Cap Fréhel (8,5 km from Fréhel and on the commune of Plévenon) is the end of the 5th stage of the 2011 Tour de France. Category:Communes in Côtes-d'Armor
title: Fréhel, Côtes-d'Armor
